# Facet Loader - Smart Context-Based Loading

## TRIGGER
ALWAYS ACTIVE - Loads relevant facets based on detected context.

## PURPOSE
Token optimization: Load only relevant facets instead of all 35 rules.

## FACETS AVAILABLE

### Web Minimalist
**File:** `facets/web-minimalist.facet`
**Description:** HTML/CSS/JS minimalism and anti-bloat patterns
**Domains:** html, css, javascript
**Load when:** User mentions html, css, javascript or minimalism, semantic design, maintainability

### Backend Pragmatic
**File:** `facets/backend-pragmatic.facet`
**Description:** Backend development patterns and best practices
**Domains:** c#, asp.net, api
**Load when:** User mentions c#, asp.net, api or architecture, patterns, standards

### Code Generators
**File:** `facets/generators.facet`
**Description:** Scaffolding and code generation tools
**Domains:** tooling, automation
**Load when:** User mentions tooling, automation or generation, scaffolding

### Quality Tools
**File:** `facets/quality-tools.facet`
**Description:** Code quality and maintenance tools
**Domains:** debugging, maintenance
**Load when:** User mentions debugging, maintenance or refactoring, analysis

### External Integrations
**File:** `facets/integrations.facet`
**Description:** External service and API integrations
**Domains:** apis, services
**Load when:** User mentions apis, services or integration, connectivity

### Process Workflows
**File:** `facets/workflows.facet`
**Description:** Process automation and workflow management
**Domains:** automation, process
**Load when:** User mentions automation, process or workflow, automation

## LOADING LOGIC

When user request detected:
1. Analyze request for domain keywords
2. Load matching facets (1-3 facets typically)
3. If no match, load all facets

**Token savings:** 5-8 KB per request vs 30 KB loading all rules
